Pretense Compliance Standards
=============================

Copyright (c) 2026 Jimmy Malhan. Licensed under the MIT License (see LICENSE).

The `pretense_compliance_standards/` package and `tests/test_pcs.py` are a graded,
fully SYNTHETIC data-loss-prevention / compliance test suite that scores how the
pretense.ai firewall (identify + mutate) and a reference detector handle regulated
data categories across major compliance frameworks.

Data disclaimer
---------------
ALL data in this repository is SYNTHETIC and fake by construction
(reserved/never-issued identifier ranges, example.com emails, test-mode secret
prefixes, Luhn-valid-but-random card numbers). Every generated corpus file carries
a "SYNTHETIC — FAKE COMPLIANCE TEST DATA, NOT REAL" banner. No value maps to a real
person, account, or secret. It is scanner test input for measuring detection
coverage — never real regulated data.
